metadata.name: Sweet Moment
metadata.description:
At that moment, time stops and sweetness envelops the environment, like the intoxicating aroma of a rose in full bloom. In that transcendental connection, the limits of the physical disappear and make their way towards the invisible, towards the realms where the true meanings reside.

Digital Art by Katassa Art 2023.
Dimensions 4000 x 4000 pixels.
